#, fuzzy
msgid "All data was collected with https://dev.java/learn/jvm/jfr/[JDK Flight Recorder], https://github.com/sysstat/sysstat[pidstat] (`-t -u -w`), and https://github.com/Hyperfoil/Hyperfoil[Hyperfoil]. The benchmark, methodology, and data are public: see https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/issues/591[issue #591] and https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/issues/420[issue #420]. The benchmark code is at https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/tree/38345ca[commit 38345ca]."
msgstr "Todos los datos se recopilaron con link:https://dev.java/learn/jvm/jfr/[JDK Flight Recorder] , link:https://github.com/sysstat/sysstat[pidstat] ( `-t -u -w` ) e link:https://github.com/Hyperfoil/Hyperfoil[Hyperfoil] . La prueba de rendimiento, la metodología y los datos son públicos: véanse link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/issues/420[las incidencias] n. link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/issues/591[º 591] y n. link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/issues/420[º 420] . El código de la prueba de rendimiento se encuentra en link:https://github.com/quarkusio/spring-quarkus-perf-comparison/tree/38345ca[la confirmación 38345ca] ."
